&lt;p&gt;This is better done at the start of the project, otherwise you’re looking at a lot of refactoring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First and foremost is to put the font file in your assets folder of your app.
If you can’t find one, just go ahead and create one in the ‘main’ folder of your app.
